# Day 01 - Networking Basics

## 🌐 What is a Network?
A network is a group of connected devices that can share data and resources.

## 🌍 What is the Internet?
The Internet is a global network that connects millions of devices worldwide.

## 📡 Types of Networks
- LAN (Local Area Network) – Small area (home, college)
- MAN (Metropolitan Area Network) – City level
- WAN (Wide Area Network) – Large area (Internet)

## 💡 Key Point
Networking is the foundation of cybersecurity.
